			        SelectedUnit = "Thousands (K)", FORMAT(DIVIDE([Quantity Total], 1000), "0.00") & " K",
			        SelectedUnit = "Lakhs (L)", FORMAT(DIVIDE([Quantity Total], 100000), "0.00") & " L",
			        SelectedUnit = "Numbers (N)", FORMAT (DIVIDE ( [Quantity Total], 1 ), "0.00" ),
			        FORMAT(DIVIDE([Quantity Total], 100000), "0.00") & " L" 
			    )
			
			```
